FBIS3-13495 "drnes050dd_94012" FBIS-NES-94-050 Document Type:Daily Report 11 Mar 1994 Palestinian Affairs Hamas Issues `Veiled Warning' on Revenge TA1103165494 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in English 1600 GMT 11 Mar 94 TA1103165494 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Islamic militants have issued a veiled warning today that revenge for the Hebron massacre might come in Brooklyn, New York. Hamas [Islamic Resistance Movement] said in a leaflet distributed in the Gaza Strip that the gunman who attacked a van of orthodox Jews in New York last week was inspired by Islamic teachings. One person was killed and three others wounded in that attack by a 28-year old Lebanese-born taxi driver.
